<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Home Page</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">

  <div class="container py-5 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-primary fw-bold">üè† Home Page</h1>
    <p class="lead text-muted mt-3">
      To access the <strong>Contact</strong> and <strong>Product</strong> pages,  
      you must add <code>?age=18</code> or greater in the URL.
    </p>

    <div class="alert alert-warning mt-4 w-75 mx-auto">
      <strong>Example URLs:</strong><br>
      <code>http://localhost:8001/contact?age=18</code><br>
      <code>http://localhost:8001/product?age=21</code>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline-primary m-2">Go to Contact</a>
      <a href="/product" class="btn btn-outline-success m-2">Go to Product</a>
    </div>

    <p class="text-muted mt-3 small">
      (If you click directly, you will stay on this Home page.  
      Add <code>?age=18</code> in the URL manually to visit Contact or Product.)
    </p>
  </div>

